- No way.
- I'll take Zi Su away from here.

61
00:04:20.190 --> 00:04:21.460
Older Bro Fei, how can we allow that?

62
00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:22.550
Hurry up and leave.

63
00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:23.870
With Lady Hong Yu here,

64
00:04:23.900 --> 00:04:25.660
