158
00:09:50.100 --> 00:09:52.860
Zi Su! Do it!

159
00:10:18.270 --> 00:10:21.290
<i>If one day, I really change</i>

160
00:10:21.290 --> 00:10:23.070
<i>and will do something that hurts you,</i>

161
00:10:23.070 --> 00:10:25.620
<i>you must leave me.</i>

162
00:10:25.620 --> 00:10:27.550
<i>You must protect yourself well.</i>

163
00:10:27.560 --> 00:10:29.050
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

164
00:10:29.050 --> 00:10:30.890
<i>What do you mean?</i>

165
00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:33.600
<i>I don't care. Just promise me first.</i>

166
00:10:33.610 --> 00:10:35.390
<i>Uh, okay, I promise you.</i>

167
00:10:35.410 --> 00:10:37.480
<i>Okay, pinky promise.</i>

