183
00:11:48.550 --> 00:11:50.110
Full of lies!

184
00:11:50.110 --> 00:11:51.590
Kill him!

185
00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:54.160
You can then become a real demon exterminator.

186
00:11:54.530 --> 00:11:57.350
